{
  "stem": "25591.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by the way, I was there now for the official reopening of the large synagogue a few months ago in September with my friend, former Prime Minister Shamir of Israel, and my friend, an enormously decent human being, the President of Hungary, President Goncz.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my friend, the Israeli Ambassador to Hungary, translated Prime Minister Shamir's speech.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Israeli Ambassador is one of the Mengele twins.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So you, you, you get chills and goose pimples as you-- as you think of these relationships and contacts.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yes, I had-- I had fistfights.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had-- the phrase [NON-ENGLISH], rotten Jew, was often used.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I, I was a very feisty boy, and I fought back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I, I had a lot of physical encounters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some I won, some I lost.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was very conscious of the fact that Jews were being squeezed commercially, educationally, culturally, in every sense.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As you know, the first anti-Jewish law after the First World War restricting the number of Jews attending university.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Numerus clausus, was passed in Hungary, not in Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was-- I was a very political boy from early on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My parents were very political.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My uncle was very political.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I read the newspapers and I, I knew all these fascist, semi-fascist, anti-Semitic, right-right political leaders.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They, they were part of my upbringing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I can sing you some bawdy songs about these various fascist bastards who my parents taught me to hate.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I, I remember the first newspaper I bought, I bought, was coming back from school the day Hitler marched into Austria, the day of the Anschluss.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the newspapers, in banner headlines, said, Hitler marches into Austria.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I was coming back from school, and I was 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
